cmark.labl: 1 for first in each country series

wars.labl: # wars in progress in country year

war.labl: 1 if war ongoing in country year

warl.labl: lagged war, w/ 0 for start of country series

aim.labl: 1 = rebels aim at center, 3 = aim at exit or autonomy, 2 = mixed or ambig.

casename.labl: Id for case, usually name of rebel group(s)

gdpen.labl: gdp/pop based on pwt5.6, wdi2001,cow energy data

gdpenl.labl: lagged gdpenl, except for first in country series

lpopl1.labl: log population, lagged except for first in country series

region.labl: country's region, based on MAR project

ethfrac.labl: ethnic frac. based on Soviet Atlas, plus est's for missing in 1964

ef.labl: ethnic fractionalization based on Fearon 2002 APSA paper

plural.labl: share of largest ethnic group (Fearon 2002 APSA)

second.labl: share of 2nd largest ethnic group (Fearon 2002 APSA)

polity2l.labl: lagged polity2, except 1st in country series

instab.labl: > 2 change in Polity measure in last 3 yrs

empwarl.labl: warl coded for data with empires

emponset.labl: onset coded for data with empires

empolity2l.labl: polity2l adjusted for empires (see fn38 in paper)

cowwarl.labl: 1 if COW war ongoing in last period

sdwarl.labl: 1 if S/D war ongoing in last period

colwarl.labl: 1 if C/H war ongoing in last period
